44Ac 10:33 So I sent for you immediately, and it was good of you to come. Now we are all here in the presence of God to listen to everything the Lord has commanded you to tell us."
44Ac 10:34 Then Peter began to speak£º "I now realize how true it is that God does not show favoritism
