44Ac 10:42 He commanded us to preach to the people and to testify that he is the one whom God appointed as judge of the living and the dead.
44Ac 10:43 All the prophets testify about him that everyone who believes in him receives forgiveness of sins through his name."
44Ac 10:44 While Peter was still speaking these words, the Holy Spirit came on all who heard the message.
