44Ac 12:14 When she recognized Peter's voice, she was so overjoyed she ran back without opening it and exclaimed, "Peter is at the door!"
44Ac 12:15 "You're out of your mind," they told her. When she kept insisting that it was so, they said, "It must be his angel."
44Ac 12:16 But Peter kept on knocking, and when they opened the door and saw him, they were astonished.
