541Tm 6:15 which God will bring about in his own time--God, the blessed and only Ruler, the King of kings and Lord of lords,
541Tm 6:16 who alone is immortal and who lives in unapproachable light, whom no one has seen or can see. To him be honor and might forever. Amen.
