552Tm 1:11 And of this gospel I was appointed a herald and an apostle and a teacher.
552Tm 1:12 That is why I am suffering as I am. Yet I am not ashamed, because I know whom I have believed, and am convinced that he is able to guard what I have entrusted to him for that day.
552Tm 1:13 What you heard from me, keep as the pattern of sound teaching, with faith and love in Christ Jesus.
552Tm 1:14 Guard the good deposit that was entrusted to you--guard it with the help of the Holy Spirit who lives in us.
552Tm 1:15 You know that everyone in the province of Asia has deserted me, including Phygelus and Hermogenes.
