601Pt 5:2 Be shepherds of God's flock that is under your care, serving as overseers--not because you must, but because you are willing, as God wants you to be; not greedy for money, but eager to serve;
601Pt 5:3 not lording it over those entrusted to you, but being examples to the flock.
